metadata.name: TopWomen
metadata.created_by: Boston Consulting Group x Manager Magazin
metadata.description:
The strategy consultancy Boston Consulting Group (BCG) and the business magazine "manager magazin" have honored the "most influential women in German business" of 2021.

BCG and Manager Magazin created this NFT in cooperation with the Berlin based Illustrator Nina Tiefenbach, who has a special penchant for female faces. She draw portraits of the 100 TopWomen and this NFT is a special present to all of the nominees.
